The evidence with the title 'Obamacare support: when polls mention repeal it seals the deal ... ' says May 23, 2017  ... They wanted to know whether different wording in survey questions would predict support for "Obamacare." Support for Obamacare is significantly higher -- by about 9  ... That term don't show higher support for getting rid of the law.  ... Poll shows majority of floridians want to keep or expand obamacare. 
